Somebody recently mentioned to me that he was looking for a belly pan for
his bus. I, too, looked for such a thing when I first got mine, but was told
by several mechanics that no such thing existed. This gentleman I've been
talking to said he'd hear that "68-72's had
>them, but it might have been the '60-70's." He also said he'd heard that
>those belly pans had problems rusting. Does anybody else have some input on
>this? I'd love to get something under there to protect the mechanics of the
>bus, even if it would rust away itself.

Rick Bailey
